data.description: Welcome home to this charming ranch nestled into a quiet cul-de-sac in the Sangaree community. The open floor plan is great for entertaining! Family room boasts of gleaming floors with a gas log fireplace that over looks the nice size kitchen with all stainless steel appliances conveying. The primary bedroom features a walk in closet and garden tub/shower combo. Enjoy grilling out this summer in your generous size fenced in back yard. Property is conveniently located next to I-26 and just a few minutes drive to dining, entertainment, and plently of shopping.
